'''《极速前进20》'''（{{lang|en|'''''The Amazing Race 20'''''}}），是[[哥倫比亞廣播公司|CBS]]的流行真人競賽節目《[[极速前进|极速前进]]》的第二十季。本季會繼續有十一對有各種既定關係的參賽者，為最終大獎——一百萬美元進行環球旅行競賽。

第二十季於2012年2月19日在CBS上首播，<ref name="EW.com">{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/12/15/cbs-announces-return-of-the-amazing-race/|title=CBS announces return of 'The Amazing Race'|last=Lynette|first=Rice|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|date=2011-12-15|accessdate=2012-01-28|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627014617/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/12/15/cbs-announces-return-of-the-amazing-race/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvline.com/2012/01/cbs-amazing-race-20-cast/#291771-0-TAR20cast|title=Amazing Race 20 Cast Includes Big Brother Duo, a Guy Named 'Fitness' and a Couple of Clowns|last=Mitovich|first=Matt|publisher=TVLine|date=2012-01-25|accessdate=2011-01-28|archive-date=2012-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319220119/http://www.tvline.com/2012/01/cbs-amazing-race-20-cast/#291771-0-TAR20cast|dead-url=no}}</ref>播出十一集後於2012年5月6日完季（最後一集為兩小時連播）。<ref name="HPost" />

已婚組合Rachel & Dave是《極速前進》第二十季的冠軍，他們同時亦成為《極速前進》美國版本有史以來單季賽段冠軍最多的組合，共嬴得八個賽段。

==製作==

===發展及拍攝===
CBS在2011年6月16日续订了《极速前进》的第二十個季度。<ref name = "Futon Critic">{{cite web|url = http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/06/16/the-amazing-race-to-make-its-20th-trek-around-the-globe-606013/20110616cbs01/2011/06/16/the-amazing-race-to-make-its-20th-trek-around-the-world-february-19/101916/|title = "The Amazing Race" to Make Its 20th Trek Around the Globe|publisher = The Futon Critic|date = 2011-06-16|accessdate = 2011-06-16}}</ref>此季將會跨越五個大陸、二十二座城市，進行四萬哩的旅程，並首次去到[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]（Paraguay）和[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]（Azerbaijan）。除了已確定會去到這兩個國家之外，本季亦已肯定會抵達[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]、[[坦桑尼亞|坦桑尼亞]]、日本、印度、[[意大利|意大利]]以及[[德國|德國]]。<ref name = "TAR20">{{cite web|url = http://www.eonline.com/news/watch_with_kristin/amazing_race_announces_season_20_cast/289019|title = The Amazing Race Announces Season 20 Cast: Big Brother's Rachel & Brendon Are at It Again!|publisher = [[E!|E!]]|last = Moorhouse|first = Drusilla|date = 2012-01-25|accessdate = 2012-01-25|archive-date = 2012-05-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120510115123/http://www.eonline.com/news/watch_with_kristin/amazing_race_announces_season_20_cast/289019|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name = "N2">{{cite web|url = http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/01/25/amazing-race-20-rachel-brendon-big-brother-new-cast/|title = 'The Amazing Race': Rachel and Brendon from 'Big Brother' head up new cast|publisher = ''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''|last = Ross|first = Dalton|date = 2012-01-25|accessdate = 2012-01-25|archive-date = 2013-05-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130511043245/http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/01/25/amazing-race-20-rachel-brendon-big-brother-new-cast/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://blogs.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment_tv_tvblog/2012/01/the-amazing-race-rachel-brendon-of-big-brother-to-play.html|title = ‘The Amazing Race’: Rachel, Brendon of ‘Big Brother’ to play|publisher = ''[[Orlando_Sentinel|Orlando Sentinel]]''|last = Boedeker|first = Hal|date = 2012-01-25|accessdate = 2012-01-25|archive-date = 2012-06-